         "Hello and welcome to my online, interactive Congressional
   office....this online office will allow a one-stop shop for many
   important constituent services. Whether you have come to visit the site
   for business or pleasure, I hope that you will find it a valuable tool
   -- a tool that continues to further bring representation to the great
   people of the Second District of Oklahoma."



